OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779970272
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with
OL,4,Csynagogue terror attack
OL,6,FA man has been arrested in connection
OL,7,Fwith a fatal terror attack at a
OL,8,Fsynagogue in Manchester.
OL,10,FA 49-year-old man was arrested in
OL,11,FSalford on suspicion of failing to
OL,12,Fdisclose information regarding
OL,13,Fterrorist activity, contrary to S38B
OL,14,Fof the Terrorism Act 2000, Greater
OL,15,FManchester Police said.
OL,17,FThe man, who has been taken into
OL,18,Fcustody for questioning, is the eighth
OL,19,Fperson to be arrested in connection to
OL,20,Fthe attack on Heaton Park Synagogie in
OL,21,FCrumpsall in October 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
