OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779970272
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with
OL,4,Csynagogue terror attack
OL,6,FWorshippers Melvin Cravitz and Adrian
OL,7,FDaulby were killed when Jihad Al-
OL,8,FShamie, 35, a Syrian-born British
OL,9,Fcitizen, targeted the shul, in October
OL,10,F2025.
OL,12,FIt was the first fatal antisemitic
OL,13,Fterror attack in the UK since the
OL,14,FCommunity Security Trust, a British
OL,15,Fcharity which provides security and
OL,16,Fadvice to the Jewish community in the
OL,17,FUK, began recording incidents in 1984.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
