PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779970272
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with
OL,4,Csynagogue terror attack
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Rob Potts,
OL,7,Fof Counter Terrorism Policing North
OL,8,FWest, said: "The loved ones of Mr
OL,9,FDaulby and Mr Cravitz, as well as
OL,10,Fthose seriously injured in the attack,
OL,11,Fhave been updated on this latest
OL,12,Fdevelopment.
OL,14,F"We remain unwavering in our
OL,15,Fcommitment to establishing the full
OL,16,Fpicture behind the attack and getting
OL,17,Fanswers for those affected, including
OL,18,Fthe local community.
OL,26,@pD@MOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
