OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779970272
OL,3,CMan arrested in connection with
OL,4,Csynagogue terror attack
OL,6,F"We are prepared to take swift, firm
OL,7,Faction where we suspect criminal
OL,8,Foffences may have occurred.
OL,10,F"Our investigation is continuing, and
OL,11,FI would once again urge anybody who
OL,12,Fmay have information that could assist
OL,13,Fus to please contact police."
